ne;"><strong>年招生信息</strong></span></span></p><p class="p3" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 9px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;; white-space: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: justify; min-height: 14px;"><span class="s1" style="font-kerning: none;"></span><br/></p><p class="p4" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 9px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Songti SC&quot;; white-space: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(38, 38, 38); text-align: justify; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="font-kerning: none; font-family: 黑体, SimHei; font-size: 14px;"></span></p><p style="white-space: normal;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;">欢迎进入法拉古特2021年新生申请页面</span></p><p style="white-space: normal;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;">2021 年新生招募通道已开启，面向全球 11-16 岁中学生开放申请。</span></p><p class="p2" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: justify; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal;"><span style="color: rgb(23, 54, 93); font-size: 20px; font-kerning: none;"><strong><br/></strong></span></p><p><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;">Welcome to the Farragut 2021 application page.</span></p><p><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;">The recruiting channel for new students in 2021 opened, and applications are open to middle school students aged 11-16 globally.</span></p><p class="p2" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: justify; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal;"><span style="color: rgb(23, 54, 93); font-size: 20px; font-kerning: none;"><strong><br/></strong></span></p><p class="p2" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: justify; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal;"><span style="color: rgb(23, 54, 93); font-size: 20px; font-kerning: none;"><strong><img src="/data/upload/image/20210206/1612595553966419.jpg" title="1612595553966419.jpg" alt="DSC00181.jpg"/></strong></span></p><p class="p2" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: justify; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;; -webkit-text-stroke-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); white-space: normal;"><br/></p><p><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(219, 229, 241);">入学年级：</span></p><p><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;">春季学期（2021年2月底开学）：入学就读9/10/11年级</span></p><p><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;">秋季学期（2021年8月底开学）：入学就读7-12年级</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;"></span></p><p style="white-space: normal;"><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;">Entry grade:</span></p><p style="white-space: normal;"><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;">Spring semester (starting at the end of February 2021): Entrance to Grade 9/10/11</span></p><p style="white-space: normal;"><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;">Fall semester (starting at the end of August 2021): Entrance to grades 7-12</span></p><p><br/></p><p><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(219, 229, 241);">关于入学测试：</span></p><p><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;">在数学、英语、逻辑和思辨上大展身手，我们重视每一位学子的身心健康，在尊重隐私的前提下精心设计我们的互动，为每一位学子保驾护航。</span></p><p><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 16px;"></span></p><p style="white-space: normal;"><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;">About the entrance test:</span></p><p style="white-space: normal;"><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;">Please show talents in mathematics, English, logic, and speculation. We attach importance to the physical and mental health of every student.</span></p><p style="white-space: normal;"><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;">To escort every student. Our interactions are designed carefully under the rules of respecting privacy.</span></p><p style="white-space: normal;"><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;">Let our encounter happen in this Welcome to the Farragut 2021 freshman application page.</span></p><p style="white-space: normal;"><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;">让我们的相遇发生在这所致力于学生终生成长的圣地，我们期待与每一个家庭的互动</span></p><p><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;">了解更多入学信息：通过<a href="http://www.farragutdg.com/index.php?catid=44" target="_self">申请流程</a>页面下方联系方式扫码或者电话联系我们</span></p><p><br/></p><p><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;">Let our encounter happen in this holy ground dedicated to the life-lo