left;line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-top: 0pt; font-size: 11pt; color: rgb(73, 73, 73);"><strong><span class="ql-author-42766628 ql-font-microsoftyahei" style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;"><br/></span></strong></p><p line="t0zx" class="ql-align-left ql-long-42766628" style="text-align:left;line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-top: 0pt; font-size: 11pt; color: rgb(73, 73, 73);"><strong><span class="ql-author-42766628 ql-font-microsoftyahei" style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;"></span></strong></p><p><span style="font-size: 14px;">With the help of the SEL social and emotional learning framework, AFA Dongguan implements holistic education, consciously cultivating students&#39; five abilities of self-awareness, self-management, social cognition, social relations, and making responsible decisions.</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 14px;">In the mission description of AFA Dongguan, <span style="font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(242, 220, 219);">perception</span> and <span style="font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(219, 229, 241);">critical thinking</span> are put forward together as the core qualities to support the realization of the five abilities above.</span></p><p line="t0zx" class="ql-align-left ql-long-42766628" style="text-align:left;line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-top: 0pt; font-size: 11pt; color: rgb(73, 73, 73);"><strong><span class="ql-author-42766628 ql-font-microsoftyahei" style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;"><br/></span></strong><br/></p><p line="t0zx" class="ql-align-left ql-long-42766628" style="text-align:left;line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-top: 0pt; font-size: 11pt; color: rgb(73, 73, 73);"><span class="ql-author-42766628 ql-font-microsoftyahei" style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;"><br/></span></p><p line="t0zx" class="ql-align-left ql-long-42766628" style="text-align:left;line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-top: 0pt; font-size: 11pt; color: rgb(73, 73, 73);"><span class="ql-author-42766628 ql-font-microsoftyahei" style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;"><img src="/data/upload/image/20210203/1612323053174875.jpg" title="1612323053174875.jpg" alt="微信图片_20201201140852.jpg"/></span></p><p line="t0zx" class="ql-align-left ql-long-42766628" style="text-align:left;line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-top: 0pt; font-size: 11pt; color: rgb(73, 73, 73);"><span class="ql-author-42766628 ql-font-microsoftyahei" style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;"><br/></span></p><p line="t0zx" class="ql-align-left ql-long-42766628" style="text-align:left;line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-top: 0pt; font-size: 11pt; color: rgb(73, 73, 73);"><span class="ql-author-42766628 ql-font-microsoftyahei" style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;"></span></p><p line="6rsl" class="ql-align-left ql-long-42766628" style="text-align:left;line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-top: 0pt; font-size: 11pt; color: rgb(73, 73, 73);"><span class="ql-author-42766628 ql-font-microsoftyahei" style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;">要使个人成长发生，在动力上需要两个方向的努力：擦亮热情和去除阻隔。</span></p><p line="6rsl" class="ql-align-left ql-long-42766628" style="text-align:left;line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-top: 0pt; font-size: 11pt; color: rgb(73, 73, 73);"><span class="ql-author-42766628 ql-font-microsoftyahei" style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;"><br/></span></p><ul class=" list-paddingleft-2"><li><p><span style="background-color: rgb(253, 234, 218);"><strong><span style="background-color: rgb(253, 234, 218); font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 18px;">擦亮热情</span></strong></span></p></li></ul><p line="nDjA" class="ql-align-left ql-long-42766628" style="text-align:left;line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-top: 0pt; font-size: 11pt; color: rgb(73, 73, 73);"><span class="ql-author-42766628 ql-font-microsoftyahei" style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;">人生的热情与自身的价值观和使命相关，是人的言行的直接驱动力，也是个人发展的原因。它会像一个热气球一样牵引着你，帮你迈过地面上的沟沟壑壑。热情所在，再苦再累都无所畏惧。青春期孩子的热情隐藏在努力读书，打电子游戏，看小说，Cosplay，或者跟朋友聊天当中。在这些表象里，孩子的热情有可能是对家长的体谅，对自我价值的渴求，或是希望一个自由自在的空间，人与人之间和谐的氛围，等等。帮助孩子从&quot;爱好&quot;中剥离自己真正在乎的方面，就像擦亮一个水晶球。孩子从中慢慢了解自己，不在固着于某种看似&quot;偏执&quot;的方式，寻求更加积极地利用周围的资源追求自我实现。比如，他/她可以在学校的各种项目中获得彼此的体谅，找到自己的价值。</span></p><p line="nDjA" class="ql-align-left ql-long-42766628" style="text-align:left;line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-top: 0pt; font-size: 11pt; color: rgb(73, 73, 73);"><span class="ql-author-42766628 ql-font-microsoftyahei" style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;"><br/></span></p><ul class=" list-paddingleft-2"><li><p><span style="background-color: rgb(253, 234, 218);"><strong><span style="background-color: rgb(253, 234, 218); font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 18px;">去除阻隔</span></strong></span></p></li></ul><p line="WKj9" class="ql-long-42766628" style="line-height: 1.7;margin-bottom: 0pt;margin-top: 0pt;font-size: 11pt;color: #494949;"><span class="ql-author-42766628 ql-font-microsoftyahei" style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;">情感的阻隔会影响个人发展。就像你跟同学老师闹别扭，有可能干什么都没心情，就谈不上学习效率了。这种状态就像带着镣铐的舞蹈。而实际上每个坏心情的背后，都是我们被压制的热情。一个气呼呼刚跟别人吵完架的孩子，可能在乎的是一份情意，一份信任。一旦这些底层所在乎的美好被点出，孩子就会很快从中坏情绪中恢复，并加深对自己的理解，塑造自己的品格。</span></p><p><br/></p><p line="t0zx" class="ql-align-left ql-long-42766628" style="text-align:left;line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-top: 0pt; font-size: 11pt; color: rgb(73, 73, 73);"><span class="ql-author-42766628 ql-font-microsoftyahei" style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;"></span></p><p><br/></p>";s:9:"seo_title";s:0:"";s:12:"seo_keywords";s:0:"";s:15:"seo_description";s:0:"";s:6:"catdir";s:25:"Social Emotional Lea