e="1612251179125336.png" alt="微信图片_20200806155005.png" width="374" height="83" style="width: 374px; height: 83px;"/></span></strong></span></strong></p><p><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;"><br/></span></p><p><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;">我们在寻找志同道合的伙伴时，想知道你为什么希望做教育，你对教育的理念是否与法拉古特学校契合，想看到你是否具备成长性思维，开放的学习态度，和很好的合作能力。</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 14px;">When we are looking for like-minded partners, we would like to know why you want to do education, whether your concept of education fits with Farragut, and whether you have a growth mindset, an open attitude towards learning yet with a good ability to cooperate.</span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;">在专业方面，法拉古特专注于考察你是否热爱自己的学科并对自己的学科有深入的理解，以及你的专业素养，包括教学所涉及到的课程设计、教学实施、评价等不同环节的专业能力，还有你对于自身所处教学领域的专业知识和概念等的理解程度。</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 14px;">In terms of professional, Farragut focuses on examining whether you love their subject and have a thorough understanding of his subject, as well as your professional, including courses relating to teaching design, teaching implementation, and evaluation of different links such as professional ability, and you for their own professional knowledge and the teaching of concepts such as understanding.</span></p><p><br/></p><p><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;">除此之外，我们还会考察你是一位学习的引导者，还是非知识的灌输者。对以学生为中心的教育中，如何引领学生成为积极主动的学习者，而非被迫强压的接收者。挖掘学生的个人潜力，培养学生的兴趣发展，让学生成为真正实现自我价值的充实个体。</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 14px;">Besides, we will examine whether you are a facilitator of learning or an indoctrinator of non-knowledge. How to guide students to be active learners rather than forced receivers in student-centered education? Excavate students&#39; personal potential, cultivate students&#39; interest and development, and make students become full individuals who truly realize their self-worth.</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 14px;"><br/></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 14px;"><img src="/data/upload/image/20210206/1612601586159378.jpg" title="1612601586159378.jpg" alt="DSC00460.jpg"/></span></p><p><br/></p><p><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">我们面向全球、全行业召集热爱教育的教师</span></p><p><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;"><strong><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; color: black; background: white; font-weight: normal;">请有意加入者发送简历至邮箱：hr@farragutdg.com</span></strong></span></p><p><br/></p>";s:9:"seo_title";s:0:"";s:12:"seo_keywords";s:0:"";s:15:"seo_description";s:0:"";s:6:"catdir";s:7:"Join Us";s:4:"http";s:3:"###";s:5:"items";s:1:"0";s:9:"listorder";s:1:"0";s:6:"ismenu";s:1:"1";s:6:"ispost";s:1:"0";s:6:"verify";s:1:"0";s:6:"islook";s:1:"0";s:7:"listtpl";s:0:"";s:7:"showtpl";s:0:"";s:7:"pagetpl";s:9:"page.html";s:8:"pagesize";s:2:"10";s:2:"yw";s:7:"Join Us";s:3:"xin";s:0:"";s:5:"topid";s:1:"6";s:11:"allchildids";s:7:"6,41,42";s:3:"url";s:18:"/index.php?catid=6";}i:15;a:29:{s:5:"catid";s:2:"15";s:6:"typeid";s:1:"4";s:7:"modelid";s:2:"10";s:8:"parentid";s:1:"0";s:5:"child";s:1:"0";s:8:"childids";s:2:"15";s:7:"catname";s:12:"报名管理";s:5:"image";s:0:"";s:7:"content";s:0:"";s:9:"seo_title";s:0:"";s:12:"seo_keywords";s:0:"";s:15:"seo_description";s:0:"";s:6:"catdir";s:13:"baomingguanli";s:4:"http";s:0:"";s:5:"items";s:1:"0";s:9:"listorder";s:1:"0";s:6:"ismenu";s:1:"0";s:6:"ispost";s:1:"0";s:6:"verify";s:1:"0";s:6:"islook";s:1:"0";s:7:"listtpl";s:0:"";s:7:"showtpl";s:0:"";s:7:"pagetpl";s:10:"page1.html";s:8:"pagesize";s:2:"10";s:2:"yw";s:0:"";s:3:"xin";s:0:"";s:5:"topid";s:2:"15";s:11:"allchildids";s:2:"15";s:3:"url";s:19:"/index.php?catid=15";}i:25;a:29:{s:5:"catid";s:2:"25";s:6:"typeid";s:1:"2";s:7:"modelid";s:1:"0";s:8:"parentid";s:1:"2";s:5:"child";s:1:"0";s:8:"childids";s:2:"25";s:7:"catname";s:24:"法拉古特东莞校区";s:5:"image";s:0:"";s:7:"content";s:3201:"<p s